        <div class="feed-time">09:42</div>
        <div class="feed-agent">01 · Confluence</div>
        <div class="feed-desc">Drafted activation page <strong>Originals × Wales Bonner FW26</strong> — formatted to template, ready to publish</div>
        <div class="feed-status"><span class="dot run"></span> Running</div>
        <a class="feed-link" href="#">Open →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="feed-row">
        <div class="feed-time">09:36</div>
        <div class="feed-agent">02 · Cropper</div>
        <div class="feed-desc">adigen cropped <strong>312 master files</strong> for adidas.com hero takeover</div>
        <div class="feed-status"><span class="dot" style="background:var(--green)"></span> Done</div>
